dc_title_s: Cities Service road map of Indiana
dc_description_s: Includes place name index on recto.; Great Lakes mileage chart, Road map of east central United States, and ancillary maps of Indianapolis, Ind., Evansville, Ind., Ft. Wayne, Ind., Gary, Ind., Muncie, Ind., South Bend, Ind., and Terre Haute, Ind. on verso. Scale approximately 1:750,000
